issue.title: Validate artifacts only shows 12 of 16 artifacts

content.raw: This is likely a limitation of how the artifact validator is implemented.  If the artifact list in the launch file isn’t the same as the one in the world sdf file, this can happen.  I’ll see if I can fix it, or at least warn that there is a difference.
